        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer222799805" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6635986625746090242">I enjoyed listening to the audio tape of this book being read by the author. His account of events in Zimbabwe since the 2008 election debacle paint a very bleak picture. It is hard to listen to some of the stories of the atrocities that were committed -- there was just so much and to such a degree that it was difficult to even wrap my brain around it. As hard as it is to hear the stories of the victims of the Mugabe regime, I felt like I had an obligation to hear their story, so that their suff</span>
  <span id="freeText6635986625746090242" style="display:none">I enjoyed listening to the audio tape of this book being read by the author. His account of events in Zimbabwe since the 2008 election debacle paint a very bleak picture. It is hard to listen to some of the stories of the atrocities that were committed -- there was just so much and to such a degree that it was difficult to even wrap my brain around it. As hard as it is to hear the stories of the victims of the Mugabe regime, I felt like I had an obligation to hear their story, so that their suffering was not in vain -- that it is at least recognized. I would recommend this book to anyone interested in learning more about the complete rape of Zimbabwe and its people by Mugabe and his cronies. The extent to which the international community has stood by and allowed these events to take place is nothing short of shameful.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6635986625746090242" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

